metadata.name: E-Spaceship #02018
metadata.description: The spaceship NFT in Genesis minting round includes three VANTERs and one Rainbow Goggles.After opening the VIM Ecosystem, only VANTER (NFT) can be acquired in spaceships summoned by the Users.The White spaceship NFT is a NFT that can be exchanged for three common VANTERs (NFT) and one rare Rainbow Goggles (NFT), and when replaced, Spaceship NFT will be incinerated. The reward boost for rare Rainbow Goggles is 10 to 19%.After minting, Rainbow Goggles with rare class or higher are not sold, only through level-up and grade-up.
